A high-fidelity macro studio product visualization cross-section cutaway of a solid-state micro-channel fluidic computing block. The monolithic body is composed of a completely transparent, optical-grade SLA UV tough engineering photopolymer resin substrate, revealing clean internal micro-fluidic trace pathways with a depth of 2.2mm. Fine lines of fluorescent index-matched tracking fluid fill the logic chambers, highlighting bistable split channels and feedback loops. The outer registry mounts show zero warp defects against a matte carbon fiber background, realistic studio cross-lighting, photorealistic material and resin textures, 8k --ar 16:9
